<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fluvial processes rather than fire primarily disturb stands of this alliance. However, the rhizomatous nature of <i>Anemopsis californica </i> and <i>Solidago </i>spp. enable plants to regenerate quickly after a fire.</div>
